    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hi, sorry to hijack this conversation but i think this could be helpful:\r\nThe easiest way to solve this is by using [webpack externals](https://webpack.js.org/configuration/externals/) in your projects:\r\n\r\n```\r\nexternals: {\r\n    'vue-server-renderer/basic': 'vue-server-renderer/basic'\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nIn a Laravel Mix configuration file you can do so like this:\r\n\r\n```\r\nmix.webpackConfig({\r\n        externals: {\r\n            'vue-server-renderer/basic': 'vue-server-renderer/basic'\r\n        }\r\n})\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2020-11-06T17:14:51Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5394#issuecomment-1367968910",
